by hitch hiking[edit] hitch hiking in india is very easy due to the enormous number of cargo trucks on every highway and road. most drivers do not speak english or any other international language; however, most have a very keen sense of where the cities and villages are located along the road. it is rare for any of them to expect payment. it might not be advisable for women to hitch hike alone in india. by auto-rickshaw[edit] a typical indian autorickshaw, andaman islands the auto-rickshaw, sometimes abbreviated as "auto" and sometimes as "rickshaw", is the most common means of hired 